
 *** version 7.0.1 - 2018-09-03
	* Maintenance update
	* Bring back module menu pages from «billing» to «accountancy»
	  section in the top menu
	* The module now depends on «modComptabilite» internal module

 *** version 7.0.0 - 2018-08-28
	* Maintenance update - drop support for dolibarr < 7
	* Move module from «accountancy» to «billing» top menu
	* Update description file with newest one coming from
	  dolibarr 7, and update code accordingly
	* Minor fixs

 *** Version 3.8.1
	* Maintenance update
	* Fix invoices links into partial payments distribution table
	    after dolibarr >= 6.0.0 (thanks to Nicholas WASTELL)
	* Update en_US language file (again thanks to Nicholas WASTELL)

 *** Version 3.8.0
	* Maintenance update
	* Fix « delete year » button in module configuration
	* Add support to multicompany third party module
	    (thanks to Sylvain Legrand)
	* Change round type to « round » for each category
	    after 1st jan. 2016
	* Improve details page. Add table showing estimated
	    loads by month
	* Fix print link on details page.

 *** Version 3.7.2
	* Allow to define taxes with more accurate values
	* Fix call to undefined function money_format()
	     (not available on Windows)

 *** Version 3.7.1
	* Major update. Rewrote most of the module. New features
	* Add ability to define taxs splitted into 4 predefined categories
	* Rewrote how estimated loads are calculated
	* Due to rewriting, some minor and rare bugs were fixed
	* Add estimated loads details page

 *** Version 3.5.3
	* Remove extra spaces from sql file
	* Add (untranslated) en_US lang skeleton file
	* Allow to run module from a custom directory
	* Minor changes

 *** Version 3.4.1
	* Module ID update
	* Fix for potential «header already sent» warnings

 *** Version 3.3.2
	* Initial version

